<p>To this end, we develop ML &amp; AI algorithms to estimate and predict events in various healthcare scenarios using data ranging from biomarker time series to hospital EHR. With the help of clinicians, patients and researchers, we also embed and deploy the proposed methods in hospitals &amp; clinical trials, promoting AI from papers to healthcare systems to make real impact in improving humanâ€™s wellbeing.</p>

<p>We are located at <a href="https://www.ucl.ac.uk/">University College London (UCL)</a>, the birthplace of Deepmind, and have close collaborations with NHS hospitals (<a href="https://www.uclh.nhs.uk/">UCLH</a>, etc). Our Institute is home to a unique range of expertise and talent resulting in highly impactful, world-changing research using large scale data and advanced analytics.</p>

<p><strong>We are  looking for passionate new PhD students, Postdocs, and Master students to join the team</strong> <a href="https://ai4hucl.github.io/ai4h_webs/vacancies">(more info)</a> <strong>!</strong></p>

<p>We are grateful for funding from NHS-X, Rosetrees Trust, UKRI CDT, and UCL Hospital and Great Ormond Street Hospital.</p>

